// defining functions 
/* collection of statements grouped together to perform an operation
 if you use void , no need to return
 
 int findArea(int Length, int Breadth){
 (Return Type, function name, required parameters)
 return Length*Breadth;
 }
 */
 
 /* properties of function in dart
 1.function in Dart are Objects.
 2. all functions in dart returns a value 
 3. if no return value is specified , then it will return null
 4. use void at front of function is not must, you can skip it also.
*/

